{
  "stem": "17426.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the international Jewish [INAUDIBLE] and the international Jewish banking and international Jewish-- everything was Jewish was bad, until finally I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I told Otto Britn, who was our lageraltester at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Grimm was demoted at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It wasn't-- they weren't very long, these, these, these lageraltester.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They could only exist for a while till a whim came and the SS men's-- one SS men's mind, and he said, oh, he's no good.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Let's take such and such.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The higher they rose, the faster they fell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the deeper they fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Goldberg, for example, died in-- in a coal mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I spoke with Otto Britn, who was German, but an inmate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was a nice man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I have his photograph as well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I saw him after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- I told him this story, that he comes in and he cleans his fingernails with my instruments.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he is torturing me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, oh, we got him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He cleans his fingernails with the instruments?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, we got him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, one day I'm going to tell the lagerfuhrer, Otto Moll.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, you're crazy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's gonna kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, Otto Moll and I were already well-known.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He would never kill me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I-- I was-- I wasn't quite convinced.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, one day he called me and he called Heinze.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said to me, I understand that the unterscharfuhrer comes in your dental station and cleans his fingernails with your instruments, sterilized instruments.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yes, Herr Lagerfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what do you have to say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He turned to the Heinze.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What do you have to say?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
